\c 7
\s Muporofita anoratidzwa mhashu nomoto norwonzi rwokuyera narwo
\p
\v 1 Hezvi zvandakaratidzwa nalshe Jehovha. Tarira, akawumba mhashu, mabukira okupedzisira achitanga kubukira; tarirai, akange ari mabukira okupedzisira kukohwa kwamambo kwapera.
\v 2 Zvino dzakati dzapedza kudya uswa bwenyika, ndikati, Aiwa, Ishe Jehovha, chikanganwirai henyu; Jakove angamira seiko, zvaari mudiki?
\p
\v 3 Jehovha akazvidya mwoyo pamusoro pechinhu ichi, Jehovha akati, Hazvingaitwi.
\p
\v 4 Hezvi zvandakaratidzwa naIshe Jehovha. Tarirai, Ishe Jehovha akadana moto kuti arwe nawo; akapedza gungwa rakadzika, akavavarira kudya nenyikawo.
\v 5 Ipapo ndakati, Aiwa, Ishe Jehovha, chiregai henyu; Jakove angamira seiko, zvaari mudiki?
\p
\v 6 Jehovha akazvidemba pamusoro pechinhu ichi, Ishe Jehovha akati, Nezvizviwo hazvingaitwi.
\p
\v 7 Hezvi zvaakandiratidza, tarirai, Ishe akange amire pamadziro akange akaitwa norwonzi rwokuyera narwo, akabata rwonzi rwokuyera muruoko rwake.
\v 8 Jehovha akati kwandiri, Amosi unooneiko? Ini ndikati, Rwonzi rwokuyera narwo. Zvino Ishe akati, Tarirai, ndichaisa rwonzi rwokuyera pakati pavanhu vangu vaIsraeri, handichatongovadarikizve,
\v 9 nzvimbo dzakakwirira dzaIsaka dzichaitwa matongo, uye nzvimbo tsvene dzaIsraeri dzichaparadzwa; ndichamukira imba yaJerobhoami
\s Amazia anoramba shoko raAmosi paBhetieri
\p
\v 10 Zvino Amazia mupristi weBhetieri akatuma nhume kuna Jerobhoami mambo waIsraeri, achiti, Amosi akarangana pakati peimba yaIsraeri kukuurayai; nyika haigoni kufara namashoko ake ese.
\v 11 Nokuti Amosi anoti, Jerobhoami achaurawa nomunondo, Israeri vachatapwa zvirokwazvo vachibviswa panyika yavo.
\p
\v 12 Amazia akatiwo kuna Amosi, Iwe muoni, enda, utizire kunyika yaJudha, undodyapo zvokudya, uporofitepo;
\v 13 asi urege kuzoporofitazve paBhetieri; nokuti inzvimbo tsvene yamambo, iimba yamadzimambo.
\p
\v 14 Ipapo Amosi akapindura, akati kuna Amazia, Ini ndakange ndisi muporofita, ndakange ndisi mwanakomana womuporofita; asi ndakange ndiri mufudzi nomurimi wemionde,
\v 15 Jehovha akanditora ndichitevera makwai, Jehovha akati kwandiri, Enda, undoporofita kuvanhu vangu vaIsraeri.
\v 16 Zvino iwe chinzwa shoko raJehovha, iwe unoti, Rega kuporofita pamusoro paIsraeri, rega kudonhedza shoko pamusoro peimba yaIsaka;
\v 17 naizvozvo zvanzi naJehovha, Mukadzi wako achava chifeve muguta, vanakomana vako navanasikana vako vachaparadzwa nomunondo, uye nyika yako ichaganhurwa norwonzi rwokuyera narwo; iwe womene uchafira munyika isakanaka, uye vaIsraeri vachatapwa zvirokwazvo vachibviswa panyika yavo.
